name: #1. PETER "THE BREAKER" PORCELAIN
description:
Elegant on the outside. Tough on the inside. This Mad Hatter ain't no tea totaler.

Inspired by the beautiful designs of porcelain pottery traditionally from China. Depending on your wallet address, the design will either be blue on white, or white on blue.

"A cat without a grin, but a grin without a cat."
"What has 13 hearts, but no other organs"
"What is broken when spoken?"

'r' toggles auto-rotate. 'l' toggles cursor following.

Artist: Yazid
